isition at Anduril (20+ years expertise scaling early talent strategies). Company actively hiring Emerging Talent Recruiters for SWE roles and running structured early career programs/bootcamps. Excellent high-signal addition for tech/engineering early talent at defense tech scale-up.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"C0115\",\n      \"name\": \"Lockheed Martin\",\n      \"category\": \"Aerospace / Defense\",\n      \"sector\": \"defense\",\n      \"description\": \"Lockheed Martin builds aircraft, missiles, spacecraft, sensors, and mission systems for U.S. defense, civil agencies, and allied security customers.\",\n      \"hq_location\": \"Bethesda, MD\",\n      \"priority\": 2,\n      \"size_estimate\": \"120k+\",\n      \"has_intern_program\": true,\n      \"linkedin_company_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/company/lockheed-martin/\",\n      \"linkedin_url_verified\": true,\n      \"recruiter_search_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/search/results/people/?keywords=Lockheed%20Martin%20recruiter\",\n      \"careers_url\": \"\",\n      \"recruiters\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"Nicole Querry\",\n          \"title\": \"Early Career Recruiter\",\n          \"linkedin_url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicole-querry-1965a4a8\",\n          \"email\": \"\",\n          \"location\": \"Owego, New York, United States\",\n          \"focus_area\": \"Early Career / University Recruiting (engineering & operations)\",\n          \"connected\": false,\n          \"messaged\": false,\n          \"responded\": false,\n          \"date_contacted\": \"\",\n          \"notes\": \"Current Early Career Recruiter at Lockheed Martin. Strong dedicated title with focus on early career talent acquisition for a major defense contractor (SWE/eng intern and new grad pipelines).\"\n        },\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
