ed Warfare hiring initiatives.'\n    }\n  ],\n  C0115: [\n    {\n      name: 'Aesha Shah',\n      title: 'University Recruiter',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/aeshashah0712',\n      location: 'Piscataway, NJ, United States',\n      focus_area: 'University Recruiting / Early career hiring',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile shows Lockheed Martin and activity referencing her University Recruiter role.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'Carol Maloney-Scott',\n      title: 'Staff Engineering Recruiter',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/carol-maloney-scott',\n      location: '',\n      focus_area: 'Engineering Recruiting / Mechanical, reliability, configuration, and field-service roles',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile says recruiter for Lockheed Martin; Talent Tuesday post states Staff Engineering Recruiter focus.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'Rob Chuckran',\n      title: 'Electronics Engineering Recruiter',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/robchuckran',\n      location: 'Denver Metropolitan Area',\n      focus_area: 'Engineering Recruiting / Electronics, loads and dynamics, cleared engineering',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile says Electronics Engineering Recruiter for Lockheed Martin and includes technical hiring activity.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'Tina Scarisbrick',\n      title: 'Global TA Recruiter',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/tina-scarisbrick',\n      location: '',\n      focus_area: 'Technical Recruiting / Embedded software, AI/ML, DevOps, and cyber roles',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn Talent Tuesday post states Global TA Recruiter for Lockheed Martin hiring embedded software, AI/ML, DevOps, and cyber talent.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'Vaughn Enrique Jones',\n      title: 'Cyber Intelligence Sr. Recruiter',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/vaughn-enrique-jones-1196715',\n      location: '',\n      focus_area: 'Technical Recruiting / Software, cyber