s.'\n    }\n  ],\n  C0117: [\n    {\n      name: 'Glenda Membreno, PRC',\n      title: 'Principal Talent Acquisition Business Partner',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/glenda-membreno',\n      location: 'Chantilly, VA, United States',\n      focus_area: 'Talent Acquisition / Space Systems engineering hiring',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Northrop Grumman; activity says promoted to Principal Talent Acquisition Business Partner and references Space Systems hiring.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'Robert Cowley',\n      title: 'Talent Acquisition Business Partner',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-cowley-54712a20b',\n      location: 'Lawton, OK, United States',\n      focus_area: 'Talent Acquisition / Sentinel and engineering leadership hiring signals',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile states Talent Acquisition Business Partner with Northrop Grumman and includes engineering hiring activity.'\n    }\n  ],\n  C0254: [\n    {\n      name: 'Keven Lee',\n      title: 'Talent Acquisition / Recruiting Leader',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/kvnl',\n      location: 'Garden Grove, CA, United States',\n      focus_area: 'Talent Acquisition / Recruiting leadership and technical hiring operations',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Relativity Space and talent acquisition recommendations.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'Marisa Farney',\n      title: 'Talent Acquisition Leader',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/marisa-farney',\n      location: 'Irvine, CA, United States',\n      focus_area: 'Talent Acquisition / Recruiting strategy and technical hiring',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Relativity Space and talent acquisition leadership experience.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'Shannon Brennan',\n      title: 'Technical Talent Acquisition Specialist',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/shannon-brennan-77123113a',\n      location: 'Dothan, AL, United States',\n      focus_area: 'Technical Recruiting / NDE, vehicle manufacturing, and technical roles',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Relativity Space and technical talent acquisition background with current technical hiring activity.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'May E.',\n      title: 'Senior Recruiting / Talent Acquisition Professional',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/mayeid',\n      location: 'Los Angeles, CA, United States',\n      focus_area: 'Talent Acquisition / Vehicle manufacturing and technical team support',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Relativity Space; recommendations describe recruiting support and senior recruiting experience.'\n    },\n    {\n      name: 'Dan Sullivan',\n      title: 'Technical Recruiter / People & Talent',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/dansull',\n      location: 'Long Beach, CA, United States',\n      focus_area: 'Technical Recruiting / Engineering and People & Talent team hiring',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile says he recruits engineers at Relativity Space and shares People & Talent team hiring activity.'\n    }\n  ],\n  C0118: [\n    {\n      name: 'Monty Zema',\n      title: 'Talent Acquisition Partner',\n      linkedin_url: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/monty-zema',\n      location: 'Temecula, CA, United States',\n      focus_area: 'Talent Acquisition / Raytheon aerospace and technical recruiting',\n      notes: 'Public LinkedIn profile lists Raytheon and Talent Acquisition Partner focus; recent activity seeks a Technical Recruiter / TA Partner.'\n    }\n  ]\n};\nfunction norm(s) { return String(s || '').trim().toLowerCase(); }\nlet added = 0;\nlet touched = 0;\nfor (const [id, people] of Object.entries(additions)) {\n  const company = data.companies.find(c => c.id === id);\n  if (\"'!company) throw new Error(`Missing company ${id}`);\n  const before = company.recruiters.length;\n  const seenNames = new Set(company.recruiters.map(r => norm(r.name)));\n  const seenUrls = new Set(company.recruiters.map(r => norm(r.linkedin_url)).filter(Boolean));\n  for (const person of people) {\n    if (company.recruiters.length >= 10) break;\n    const nameKey = norm(person.name);\n    const urlKey = norm(person.linkedin_url);\n    if (seenNames.has(nameKey) || (urlKey && seenUrls.has(urlKey))) continue;\n    company.recruiters.push({\n      name: person.name,\n      title: person.title,\n      linkedin_url: person.linkedin_url,\n      email: blank.email,\n      location: person.location,\n      focus_area: person.focus_area,\n      connected: blank.connected,\n      messaged: blank.messaged,\n      responded: blank.responded,\n      date_contacted: blank.date_contacted,\n      notes: person.notes\n    });\n    seenNames.add(nameKey);\n    if (urlKey) seenUrls.add(urlKey);\n    added++;\n  }\n  if (company.recruiters.length > before) touched++;\n}\nfs.writeFileSync(file, JSON.stringify(data, null, 2) + '\"'\\\\n');\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify({ touched, added }, null, 2));\nNODE\"","aggregated_output":"","exit_code":null,"status":"in_progress"}}
